# iPXE Station Data Directory
#
# This file ensures the data directory structure is preserved in git
# while excluding the actual data files (which can be large Ubuntu ISOs).
#
# Directory structure:
# data/
# └── srv/
#     ├── tftp/    # TFTP boot files (undionly.kpxe, ipxe.efi)
#     ├── http/    # HTTP boot files (Ubuntu versions, ISOs)
#     ├── ipxe/    # iPXE scripts (boot.ipxe)
#     └── dhcp/    # DHCP configurations
#
# The actual directories will be created automatically by the deploy script
# or Docker container on first run.